ors, clerics, enchanters, and monks.  *LOLOL*  Lead a raid or two and then get back to me.<P>  <IMG SRC="mad.gif" border="0">   <IMG SRC="mad.gif" border="0"> RageFactor Co.  <IMG SRC="mad.gif" border="0">   <IMG SRC="mad.gif" border="0"> <P>Later,<BR>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
