all together.  Neither of which will occur.<P>The funny thing is they are so worried about balancing the classes out yet they are adding a whole new class, the beastlord.<P>Since they told us we should be equals we want for that to happen but with the beastlord comming out I can see many heated debates and questions occuring.<P>We'll see what the future holds for EQ...)<P>Later,<P><BR>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
