Hmmm, I'm kinda coming into this a little late, but in my experience, CC is essential for any RAID.  A raid is not just the fight with the BOSS MOB.  It's the fight with the boss mob PLUS all it took to get to him.  And sometimes, there aren't even boss mobs associated with raids.  For example, the other night I went on a joint guild raid to Kael Drakkal.  There was no boss mob we were after.  We were there for armor drops (see Thurgadin quests).  And quite frankly, without chanters there for CC (not mezzes, charms) a lot more of us would have died.  Some might not consider that a raid cuz it had no boss mob, but any time a get together with 35 peeps from 2 guilds with a hunt objective, I consider it a raid.<P>--------------------<P>Atern Gemfitter<BR>53rd 'chanter<BR>Crimson Fist<BR>Tholuxe Paells
